{"tid":2003001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★IT Delay?】CU Mask---網上登記後，會在兩日後收到成功登記短訊？？！！","createTime":"2020-05-05T13:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T12:50:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7b57168a273c66f57f69e92c507879760424bdcf","tid":2003001,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:24:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成功登記會收到確認短訊 <br />\n</span><br />\n政府資訊科技總監林偉喬表示，在網上登記後，用戶會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">在兩日後會在手機收到成功登記的短訊</span>，一般情況下兩周可以獲安排香港郵政派送以掛號方式將口罩送上門。他提醒，每個電話只能夠接受一次登記。當市民完成登記後便會獲得一個登記編號，林偉喬建議市民要留下編號，因為無論查詢時須再輸入編號。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/469215/cu-mask%E9%8A%85%E8%8A%AF%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E6%98%8E%E8%B5%B7%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98-%E6%B4%BE%E7%99%BC%E7%B4%B0%E7%AF%80-%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A0%85-%E6%B8%85%E6%B4%97%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F469215%2Fcu-mask%25E9%258A%2585%25E8%258A%25AF%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%2599%25BB%25E8%25A8%2598-%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2584%258F%25E4%25BA%258B%25E9%25A0%2585-%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25B4%2597%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B3%2595&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=54d5f92c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/469215/cu-mask%E9%8A%85%E8%8A%AF%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E6%98%8E%E8%B5%B7%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98-%E6%B4%BE%E7%99%BC%E7%B4%B0%E7%AF%80-%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A0%85-%E6%B8%85%E6%B4%97%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95</a>"},{"pid":"1961dc03d5ce67f697970238a93f19616890c419","tid":2003001,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:24:24.000Z","msg":"why need 兩日？"},{"pid":"3765eeb614020f8127a99a00c8bf1cfeafe0a7d2","tid":2003001,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd877e7790400de1f50ad6e31347e882d0bc9da","tid":2003001,"uid":62226,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:26:02.000Z","msg":"係咪用人手SEND SMS??"},{"pid":"75e141de514f04ff882692bec2754a869b750c92","tid":2003001,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"會唔會send上支那confirme，再send返來香港？所以要2日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8efd1a1484461428a378f8d7e28dbd392b129b9","tid":2003001,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:27:41.000Z","msg":"收集大家資料<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_Wq9lQZA_Xc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_Wq9lQZA_Xc&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=dd0c4809\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_Wq9lQZA_Xc</a>"},{"pid":"ea00d64c44afc877384f908c0c7bf2dc58560b5a","tid":2003001,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:28:29.000Z","msg":"普通網上登記做user都係即時confirm<br />\n<br />\n未聽過要2日，除非要check嘢"},{"pid":"34abef3965a88082c8e42cd9238269a8fb99f52b","tid":2003001,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:29:16.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"bded30c7347ec4ca42db50d751d9ff483332099b","tid":2003001,"uid":34409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"75e141de514f04ff882692bec2754a869b750c92","tid":2003001,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"會唔會send上支那confirme，再send返來香港？所以要2日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:39:09.000Z","msg":"人手print out, 再人手將資料填上表格，<br />\n之後先等Office Boy 將文件拎去相關部門處理。"},{"pid":"d3254799ebb85ce97a5346927b3092ef3ee2ddce","tid":2003001,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T01:06:50.000Z","msg":"政府向市民免費派發的可重用口罩，今早7時起接受網上登記。<br />\n<br />\n因為個短訊可能係申請失敗<br />\n<br />\n本台記者早上7時登入指定網站時，一度顯示要等候一個多小時，其後10多分鐘後可進入登記網頁。登記人需填上個人資料，包括姓名、身份證號碼、出生日期、手提電話號碼以及本港地址，網頁同時顯示可以為另外5人登記。填報所有資料後，會獲發一個登記編號，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>核實登記資料後，會以短訊通知登記結果</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府上載短片，教市民如何佩戴和清洗可重用口罩。根據片段，市民佩戴口罩時，有條紋的一面向外，較彎曲的一邊向上，如果口罩不夠貼面，可以將掛耳打結。<br />\n<br />\n用過的口罩必須每日清洗，清洗時要整個口罩洗，不要取出濾芯。要用肥皂及冷水手洗，之後用乾毛巾印乾，不能擰乾，要掛起來或平放晾乾。另外亦提醒，不應使用漂白劑、柔順劑或含螢光劑的洗衣液，也不可以熨燙。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1524484-20200506.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1524484-20200506.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=7f0742f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1524484-20200506.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=51188840\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1524484-20200506.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5858271ec2142bd40e2a3fe63970b8654d79353f","tid":2003001,"uid":47042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bded30c7347ec4ca42db50d751d9ff483332099b","tid":2003001,"uid":34409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"75e141de514f04ff882692bec2754a869b750c92","tid":2003001,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"會唔會send上支那confirme，再send返來香港？所以要2日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:39:09.000Z","msg":"人手print out, 再人手將資料填上表格，<br />\n之後先等Office Boy 將文件拎去相關部門處理。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T01:42:22.000Z","msg":"仲有人手filing <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837eb1e08e1b1a963b479071c37c33ca4d3fea1f","tid":2003001,"uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T12:50:46.000Z","msg":"笑死，政府聽日開始排CU Mask口罩個網站原來要輪候登記<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2002936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2002936</a>"}]}